OL,7,F"We had a huge amount of interest in
OL,8,Fthe book leading up to the auction and
OL,9,Fon sale day we were joined online by
OL,10,Fmore than 30 bidders from America and
OL,11,Fthe UK along with two telephone bids
OL,12,Fand people watching in the sale room.
OL,14,F"After a solid bidding battle the copy
OL,15,Fwas eventually secured by a telephone
OL,16,Fbidder in the UK.
OL,18,F"Congratulations to the winner and
OL,19,Falso to the underbidders, who all
OL,20,Fhelped make this a magical moment in
OL,21,Fthe sale room."
